Interface TreeItem

    TreeItemImpl
    public interface TreeItem
extends utam.core.framework.base.PageObject
    Selector: lightning-tree-item Represents the lightning-tree-item Lightning web component. Toggle a tree branch by clicking the toggle button. Get a tree branch or link text, URL, or href value of the link. Click the link of the tree item. Get the count of root-level items. Retrieve a specific lightning-tree-item by text value match from the lightning-tree-item. , created from JSON resources/utam/lightning/treeItem.utam.json
